  "description": "Kafka metrics from kafka-exporter (Prometheus). First panel: UP = Prometheus can scrape the exporter. If Topics discovered is empty: 1) Ensure kafka-exporter and Kafka are running (docker compose ps). 2) Set time range to Last 5 minutes. 3) Send at least one event (POST /api/events) so topic grid.events.v1 exists. 4) curl -s http://localhost:9308/metrics | grep kafka_topic_partitions to confirm exporter sees Kafka.",
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "mappings": [{"options": {"0": {"color": "red", "index": 0, "text": "DOWN"}, "1": {"color": "green", "index": 1, "text": "UP"}}, "type": "value"}, {"options": {"from": "", "to": "null", "result": {"color": "red", "index": 0, "text": "NO DATA"}}, "type": "value"}], "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "red", "value": null}, {"color": "green", "value": 1}]}, "unit": "short"}, "overrides": []},
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0},
